person stranded on an island -> 

send message via HAM radio to a certain frequency -> 
say in order 1. phone number 2. message 3. BURP (ends the call [phrase can be changed])

people on other end receive call/message -> 
python regex parses the message for phone number, message, and burp

machine picks it up -> 

sends a message to the number with the message attached -> 

people receive the text message // END 

Resources used
https://www.regular-expressions.info/
https://regex101.com/
https://www.regular-expressions.info/editpadpro.html

